{"id": "art-15311", "label": "Art. 15311", "title": "Art. 15311", "slug": "art-15311", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_431818205\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2088\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_431818205\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>11</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_747888765\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2087\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_747888765\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de supraveghere se <span class=SpellE>întrune&#351;te</span>\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o dat&#259; la 3 luni. <span\nclass=SpellE>Pre&#351;edintele</span> convoac&#259; consiliul de supraveghere <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prezideaz&#259; întrunirea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1235968782\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2086\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1235968782\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Consiliul de supraveghere este convocat în orice moment\nla cererea motivat&#259; a cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 2 dintre\nmembrii consiliului sau la cererea directoratului. Consiliul se va întruni în\ncel mult 15 zile de la convocare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1078001495\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2085\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1078001495\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span> nu\nd&#259; curs cererii de convocare a consiliului în conformitate cu <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> alin. (2), autorii cererii pot convoca ei\n<span class=SpellE>în&#351;i&#351;i</span> consiliul, stabilind ordinea de zi a\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;ei</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1700146466\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2084\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1700146466\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Membrii directoratului pot fi <span class=SpellE>convoca&#355;i</span>\nla întrunirile consiliului de supraveghere. Ei nu au drept de vot în consiliu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2003421394\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2083\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2003421394\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)La fiecare <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;&#259;</span>\nse va întocmi un proces-verbal, care va cuprinde numele <span class=SpellE>participan&#355;ilor</span>,\nordinea de zi, ordinea deliber&#259;rilor, deciziile luate, num&#259;rul de\nvoturi întrunite <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> opiniile separate.\nProcesul-verbal este semnat de c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde c&#259;tre cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> un alt membru prezent al\nconsiliului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_1908677872\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2082\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1908677872\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA\n<span class=SpellE>III:Dispozi&#355;ii</span> comune pentru sistemul unitar <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sistemul dualist</span></b></p>"}